headline: Gear Up for Keurig Dr Pepper (KDP) Q2 Earnings: Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for Keurig Dr Pepper (KDP), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended June 2025.
